   "isNew": false,
   "overview": "St. Christopher's at The Winston is right in the middle of all the action Amsterdam has to offer! The Red Light District is just outside our back garden, We're a 5-10 minute walk from Central Station, and we're 1 minute from Dam Square. The hostel serves up a rocking bar with a beer garden. \r\n\r\nThere is a continental breakfast available every morning for just \u20ac7 a day which can be purchased at reception on arrival, and free WiFi runs throughout the building. All guests receive 25% discount on food at our lively Belushi's bar and restaurant, plus great drink deals!\r\n\r\nAll guests must be 18 years or older on the day of check-in.\r\n \r\nWe have a fun, diverse, international crew; many of whom speak multiple languages and are travellers just like you. They are happy to help you plan trips and book tickets for onward travel, and there is a free walking tour that picks up from the hostel and a pub crawl that passes through our bar each night.\r\n \r\nParty or relax in our on-site Belushi's bar and restaurant where you'll find cool tunes, sports on TV, a pool-table, great food and drink promotions all year round. On our bar menu you'll find hearty and healthy food, including the best burgers in town, tasty salads, towering Nachos, killer spicy wings, and luscious wraps. And to make things even better; all hotel/hostel guests get a 25% discount on the entire food menu! Guests also get exclusive drinks deals on a great selection of spirits, beers, and shots - all day every day!\r\n\r\nThere is free Wi-Fi running smoothly throughout the entire building. \r\n \r\nCheck-in is at 15:00 and check-out at 11:00. We have a 24-hour front desk and secure coin-operated luggage storage that can be used before check-in and after check-out (max. \u20ac 6 / 24 hours)\r\n \r\nGroup bookings of 10 people or more need to be requested by email. We reserve the right to cancel group bookings which are not made in this way.\r\n\r\nThis is a strictly 18+ hostel. \r\n \r\nNon-Refundable Rate\r\nThis reservation is non-refundable. The remaining balance of your stay may be charged at any time after the booking is confirmed.\r\n\r\nFree Cancellation Rate\r\nYou may cancel your reservation free of charge up to 24 hours before the scheduled arrival date. In the event of a no-show or cancellation made within 24 hours of arrival, the full booking amount will be charged. The remaining balance of your stay may be charged within 24 hours of arrival.",
